TITLE: Installing Rector via Composer
DESCRIPTION: Command to install Rector as a development dependency in a PHP project using Composer.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
composer require rector/rector --dev
```

