TITLE: Upgrading to First Class Callable in PHP 8.1
DESCRIPTION: Converts array callable syntax to first class callable syntax using the new (...) syntax.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_227

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
 final class SomeClass
 {
     public function run()
     {
-        $name = [$this, 'name'];
+        $name = $this->name(...);
     }

     public function name()
     {
     }
 }
```

