TITLE: Converting call_user_func_array() to Variadic Function Calls in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Modernizes code by replacing call_user_func_array() with direct function calls using the spread operator (...), resulting in cleaner and more readable code.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_59

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
 class SomeClass
 {
     public function run()
     {
-        call_user_func_array('some_function', $items);
+        some_function(...$items);
     }
 }
```

