TITLE: Adding Strict Parameter Types to Private Methods (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This rector adds strict parameter types to private methods based on the types passed in method calls. It infers the type from usage and updates the method signature.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_277

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
 final class SomeClass
 {
     public function run(int $value)
     {
         $this->resolve($value);
     }

-    private function resolve($value)
+    private function resolve(int $value)
     {
     }
 }
```

