TITLE: Adding Types from Resource Docblocks (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This configurable rector adds parameter and return types based on resource docblocks, replacing @param and @return annotations with type declarations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_288

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
 class SomeClass
 {
-    /**
-     * @param resource|null $resource
-     */
-    public function setResource($resource)
+    public function setResource(?App\ValueObject\Resource $resource)
     {
     }

-    /**
-     * @return resource|null
-     */
-    public function getResource()
+    public function getResource(): ?App\ValueObject\Resource
     {
     }
 }
```

