TITLE: Converting MyCLabs Enum to Native PHP 8.1 Enum
DESCRIPTION: Refactors MyCLabs enum class to use PHP 8.1 native enum with string backing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_228

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
-use MyCLabs\Enum\Enum;
-
-final class Action extends Enum
+enum Action : string
 {
-    private const VIEW = 'view';
-    private const EDIT = 'edit';
+    case VIEW = 'view';
+    case EDIT = 'edit';
 }
```

