TITLE: Converting property assignments to constructor promotion in PHP 8.0
DESCRIPTION: Transforms simple property initialization and assignment to use constructor promotion, a new feature in PHP 8.0 that simplifies class property declarations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_215

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
 class SomeClass
 {
-    public float $price;
-
     public function __construct(
-        float $price = 0.0
+        public float $price = 0.0
     ) {
-        $this->price = $price;
     }
 }
```

