TITLE: Running Rector in Dry-Run Mode
DESCRIPTION: Command to execute Rector in dry-run mode, which displays the changes Rector would make without actually applying them.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
vendor/bin/rector src --dry-run
```

