TITLE: Adding Strict Types Declaration (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This rector adds the declare(strict_types=1) statement to PHP files if it's missing, enabling strict type checking.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_295

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
+declare(strict_types=1);
+
 function someFunction()
 {
 }
```

