TITLE: Adding Typed Property from Assignments in PHP
DESCRIPTION: The TypedPropertyFromAssignsRector adds type declarations to properties based on the types of values assigned to them. It analyzes assignment operations to determine the appropriate property type.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_324

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
```diff
 final class SomeClass
 {
-    private $name;
+    private string|null $name = null;

     public function run()
     {
         $this->name = 'string';
     }
 }
```
```

