TITLE: Converting RectorConfig to RectorConfigBuilder (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: RectorConfigBuilderRector modernizes Rector configuration from function-based to builder pattern. This simplifies configuration and makes it more expressive.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_265

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
-return static function (RectorConfig $rectorConfig): void {
-    $rectorConfig->rule(SomeRector::class);
-};
+return RectorConfig::configure()->rules([SomeRector::class]);
```

