TITLE: Converting Ternary Null Checks to Null Coalescing Operator (PHP 7.0)
DESCRIPTION: Replaces ternary expressions that check for null or isset with the null coalescing operator (??) introduced in PHP 7.0 for more concise code.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_163

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
-$value === null ? 10 : $value;
+$value ?? 10;
```

