TITLE: Replacing substring comparison with str_ends_with() in PHP 8.0 - Variable Needle
DESCRIPTION: Converts substring checks that verify string endings to use the new str_ends_with() function introduced in PHP 8.0, making code more readable and efficient.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_223

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
 class SomeClass
 {
     public function run()
     {
-        $isMatch = substr($haystack, -strlen($needle)) === $needle;
+        $isMatch = str_ends_with($haystack, $needle);

-        $isNotMatch = substr($haystack, -strlen($needle)) !== $needle;
+        $isNotMatch = !str_ends_with($haystack, $needle);
     }
 }
```

