TITLE: Replacing strpos checks with str_contains() in PHP 8.0
DESCRIPTION: Converts strpos() !== false and strstr() checks to use the new str_contains() function introduced in PHP 8.0 for more readable code.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_222

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
 class SomeClass
 {
     public function run()
     {
-        return strpos('abc', 'a') !== false;
+        return str_contains('abc', 'a');
     }
 }
```

