TITLE: Implementing null coalescing assignment operator in PHP 7.4
DESCRIPTION: Replaces the pattern of assigning a value with null coalescing operator with the new ??= operator introduced in PHP 7.4.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rectorphp/rector/blob/main/docs/rector_rules_overview.md#2025-04-16_snippet_205

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
 $array = [];
-$array['user_id'] = $array['user_id'] ?? 'value';
+$array['user_id'] ??= 'value';
```

